Uganda Appoints Ssali Deputy Managing Director of Government Pension Fund

-- B y   F r e d   O j a m b o
-- 
2011-03-21T08:00:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-21/uganda-appoints-ssali-deputy-managing-director-of-government-pension-fund.html
Ugandan Finance Minister Syda
Bbumba named Geraldine Ssali deputy managing director of the  National Social Security Fund , the country’s state pension fund,
the agency said.  Ssali has been working as the head of the directorate of
the management unit in the U.K.’s Treasury Department, the fund
said today in an e-mailed statement from the capital, Kampala.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Ojambo in Kampala at 
 fojambo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
